extends layout

block content
  h1= title
  p Welcome to #[em HallowList], an inventory management application built with Express and MongoDB.

  h2 Categories: 

    if error 
      p Error getting dynamic content 
    else 
      p The application has the following categories 

      ul 
        each category in category_list 
          li 
            a(href=category.url) #{category.name}
